entry.value: update ProcessingAudit set jobstatus=0 where date_format(audittime,'%Y%m%d%H%i')='${hdfsDate}${hdfsHour}' and domain='${domain}' and vendor='${vendor}' and emstype='${emsType}' and technology='${technology}' and module='PM'

select count(*) as emscount from EMSServer where domain='${domain}' and vendor='${vendor}' and emstype='${emsType}' and technology like '%${technology}%' and deleted =0 and pmhdfsfilepath is not null;

select count(*) as auditcount from ProcessingAudit where domain='${domain}' and vendor='${vendor}' and date_format(audittime,'%Y-%m-%d')=date_format(DATE_ADD(now(), INTERVAL 1 Day),'%Y-%m-%d') and filename not like '%.xml%' and module='PM' and emstype='${emsType}' and technology='${technology}';

select group_concat(concat(ip,'DETAILSPLITTER',hostname,'DETAILSPLITTER',port,'DETAILSPLITTER',pmusername,'DETAILSPLITTER',pmpassword,'DETAILSPLITTER',pmhdfsfilepath,'${vendor}/${emsType}/${technology}') SEPARATOR 'EMSSPLITTER') as emsDetail From EMSServer where domain='${domain}' and vendor='${vendor}' and emstype='${emsType}' and technology like '%${technology}%' and deleted =0 and pmhdfsfilepath is not null;
